            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                    <ab/>
                            <ab><persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Ghisulfus"
                            >Ghisolfo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> et <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes/Paganellus">Iohannes que Paganello</name></persName>
                        vocatur et <persName><name ref="Ildus">Ildo</name></persName> germani filii
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName>
                        ricevono in livello da <persName key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                                ><name ref="Bonifacius">Bonifacio</name></persName> filio bone
                        memorie <persName><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardi</name></persName>, una <rs
                            key="#Petiae">petia</rs> de terra tua illa, quod est <rs key="#Cereals"
                            >campo</rs> quas tu abis in loco a <placeName key="#Petiae #Cereals"
                            >Canpreiti</placeName> tenentes uno capo cum uno lato in terra <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Petiae #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti Bartholomei</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/281">Sextinghe</placeName> et
                        aliquantuluo in terra tua qui supra <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae"><name
                                ref="Bonifacius">Bonifatio</name></persName> (…), et alio capo cum
                        uno lato tene in <rs key="#Rivers">rivo</rs> de <placeName key="#Rivers"
                            >Canpreiti et vocitatur a rio Pallgi</placeName>, con tutte le sue
                        dipendenze. Si impegnano a versare pro omni censum et iustitiam a Bonifacio
                        ed eredi per omne mense ianuario (…) a <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> tua illa
                        domnicata in loco et finibus a <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/344"
                            >Caldane</placeName> il censo annuale di argentu denari boni expendibili
                        numero sex. Se non rispetteranno i suddetti impegni, promettono con i loro
                        eredi di versare a Bonifacio, ai suoi eredi e proeredi la pena argentu
                        obtimum solidos quadraginta. Chiedono a <persName key="#Writer #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Rodelandus">Rodilandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris la stesura di due
                        cartulas. Actu loco <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/355"
                            >Iuncarico</placeName> prope ipso <rs key="#Castle">castello</rs>.
                        Sottoscrive: Ego Ghisolfo presbiter in oc libello a nos facto subscripsi.
                        Testi: <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rotius">Roctii</name></persName>
                        filio item <persName><name ref="Rotius">Roctii</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Heinricus">Enrighi</name></persName> filio
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Teobaldus">Tebaldi</name></persName>;
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rusticus">Rustichi</name></persName>
                        filio bone memorie <persName><name ref="Rotius">Roctii</name></persName>.
                        Scrive: Rodilandus notarius domni imperatoris.</ab>
                        </div>
